ot compare to slow in efficacy, by at least a factor of three.<br>
<br>
This is a flaw in the design of the game which <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>PoP</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> brings to the surface.  I think this will be the subject of the next radical reformation.<br>
<br>
In the mean time, one might expect, I suppose, to see more caster mobs, which are not as effected by slow.  Alternately, more mobs will be flagged unslowable.<br>
<br>
