<br>
Sony does appear to be wanting to increase the soloing ability of other classes (Clerics /boggle), so why would they not want to maintain the same ability for Mages?  Seems like they are running around trying to make this expansion a good one, and just missed a few things. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Valaglar</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> : Cleric of 50 Blessings<br>
